<li>Ned O'Gorman, 'My dinners with Isaiah: the music of a philosopher's life - Sir Isaiah Berlin' - includes related article on Isaiah Berlin's commitment to ideals of genuine understanding over intellectual mastery, <a href="http://www.findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1252/is_n14_v125/ai_21058769/pg_1" class="external text" title="http://www.findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1252/is_n14_v125/ai_21058769/pg_1" rel="nofollow"><i>Commonweal</i>, 14 August 1998</a></li>
<li><i>Conversations with Isaiah Berlin,</i> <a href="/wiki/Ramin_Jahanbegloo" title="Ramin Jahanbegloo">Ramin Jahanbegloo</a> (1992)</li>
</ul>
<table class="wikitable" style="margin:0.5em auto; font-size:95%;clear:both;">
<tr>
