<td width="40%" style="text-align: center;" rowspan="1"><b>President of <a href="/wiki/Wolfson_College,_Oxford" title="Wolfson College, Oxford">Wolfson College, Oxford</a></b><br />
1965–1975</td>
<td width="30%" align="center" rowspan="1">Succeeded&#160;by<br />
<b><a href="/wiki/Henry_Arthur_Pears_Fisher" title="Henry Arthur Pears Fisher">Sir Henry Fisher</a></b></td>
